frame0.consensus_text: An Expresse arrived this morning that S<sw-ex>i</sw-ex><sl>r</sl> C Shovell is returned into the Downes =
By a fforreigne Maile this day wee have a l<sw-ex>ett</sw-ex>re from the Campe <sw-del>th</sw-del> that Ronstak the 9<sw-sup>th</sw-sup>
inst<sw-ex>ant</sw-ex> w<sw-ex>hi</sw-ex><sl>ch</sl> sayes wee are beseigeing Huy with 22000 men & that the D<sw-ex>uke</sw-ex> of Holstein -
Comands them the Trenches being opened the 8th & that the King goes with another
S<sw-ex>i</sw-ex><sl>r</sl> London 6th <sw-ex>Septem</sw-ex>ber 1694
Yesterday the severall Messeng<sw-ex>e</sw-ex>rs brought to Towne
10 Conspirators viz the Lord Mollineux S<sw-ex>i</sw-ex><sl>r</sl> Rich<sw-ex>ar</sw-ex>d Stanley
S<sw-ex>i</sw-ex><sl>r</sl> Thomas Clifton S<sw-ex>i</sw-ex><sl>r</sl> W<sw-ex>illia</sw-ex>m Gerrard Mr Blundell of
Craseby mr Langton of Lore mr Lee of Lime w<sw-ex>illia</sw-ex>m
Wood Rich<sw-ex>ar</sw-ex>d Iackson & John Wilson whoe as yet
continue in the Messeng<sw-ex>e</sw-ex>rs hands & this day or tomorrow
will bee examined by the Secretary of State & wee
shall quickly see whether there bee more in the
plott then Dyer in his news Letters would sham
vpon vs
A Draught of 2400 is to bee speedily
made out of the veterane forces to bee formed
into 3 Regiments to bee sent to Iamaica
The Gunners which were on
board the Expedic<sw-ex>i</sw-ex>on are come to Towne being
discharged
A Patent is passeing the seales to
make one mr Sheild son of Com<sw-ex>mand</sw-ex>er Shield the
Queens Goldsmith
There is but part of our East
Land ffleet as yet arrived, which makes our
Merchants in paine for the rest
I last told you that a fellow was
seized in St James's Parke with a Cane Gunn
whoe being Comitted to the charge of a Messenger -
made his Escape but was retaken & comitted
to the Gate house as also one one venue a late
Complotter ag<sw-ex>ains</sw-ex>t the Governm<sw-ex>en</sw-ex><sl>t</sl> whoe is also com<sw-ex>m</sw-ex>itted
to the same place
The M<sw-ex>en</sw-ex> of Warrs store shipps
& Transport shipps designed for Iamaica are
getting ready with all the dilligence & speed
imaginable
